metadata.name: #ShowYourself - You is Art
metadata.description:
This piece of art shows that colour doesn't need to be as per book. Just feel the colour and express your feeling. In art no one can judge you because the art itself is you.

#ShowYourself is my submission for Rik's Oostenbroek's creative contest.

#rikoostenbroek #aoi #showyourself

4100x5120
